                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221023-104-defend1078 t18221023-104-punish560"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and Discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
